                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1132" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM HOBBS</persName>
                  </hi>. I produce a certificate of the prisoner's conviction, by the name of John Rock—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted</hi> 20<hi rend="italic">th March</hi>, 1843, <hi rend="italic">and confined three months</hi>)—the prisoner is the man.</p>
